    "title": "京东规则动态一览（2025年8月11日-2025年8月15日）",
    "followRuleId": "1272485867063218176",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则公示】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1272119910528585728\">《京东开放平台电脑组件类目招商激励政策》&nbsp; </a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">有效销售额及广告费率符合要求后，将返还对应类目下有效销售总额的一定比例的运营支持服务费。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1272379471789428736\">《京东开放平台内存、固态硬盘、机械硬盘类目招商激励政策》</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">有效销售额及广告费率符合要求后，将返还对应类目下有效销售总额的一定比例的运营支持服务费。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1272743176179945472\">《2025年8月京东个人/个体-服饰运动、个护美妆、鞋靴箱包等类目部分POP商家销售激励政策》&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">广告投放消耗费率及销售GMV符合要求后，将返还销售金额目标对应点数的佣金至京准通。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增 】<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1273099808730648576\">《京东开放平台营养保健类目销售激励政策》&nbsp; </a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">当月销售额达到激励对应门槛，且在政策周期内环比增长达到激励条件，即可解锁对应层级佣金返还政策。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1272066989803835392\">《京东开放平台商家保证金管理规则》</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">调整月度补缴规则与风险保证金退还周期的表述。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1272537988114550784\">《京东开放平台店铺命名规则》 </a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①调整结构顺序；②调整店铺名称不得包含的内容描述；③调整店铺名或相关资质不符合规则的处置措施；④调整普通企业店命名规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">7</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订 】<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1272852705735479296\">《京东开放平台商品价格管理规则》 </a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">价格违规程度和处理措施拆分为一般、严重、特别严重三级。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">关联规则：<a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1272855299103002624\">《京东开放平台个人/个体商品管理规则》 </a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则生效】</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1270294914747469824\">《京东开放平台家电家居品类新商激励政策（2025.7.1-2025.12.31）》</a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">鼓励新商家在京东开放平台积极经营，特制定新商激励政策。入驻后快速度过冷启期、达成稳定日销、且GMV达预期的商家，会按商家实际向平台交付的佣金返还广告虚拟金。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1269591667699224576\">《京东开放平台品牌管理规则》</a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">明确品牌创建及信息要求、重复品牌管理要求、品牌发品等要求。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=590903538377428992&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\">《京东开放平台取消订单服务管理规则》</a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①更新规则适用范围；②增加基础原则；③处理标准中增加了商家需给客户及时处理的场景及节点；④细化处理时效；⑤增加和解方案；⑥不适用0秒退类目更新。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"color: #467886; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1013329543295012864\">《计价黄金克重补差&amp;质量问题售后服务管理规则》</a></span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">基于是否用克重补差系统，分场景细化管理及违约金标准等处理措施。</span></p>",
